data.name: label59.Text
data.value:
Tool named "CodeGenerator" implements the following functions :
- I/O : Pin settings - Project Path : Displays the current path - Alternative Configure: Alternative Function details - Input Configure : Input configure details - Output Configure : Output configure details
- Peripheral : Interrupt setting - Interrupt Configure : Add interrupts as required - Add All Interrupt : Interrupts configure details

data.name: label32.Text
data.value: The RH850/F1L is a product line in Renesas' RH850/F1x series of single chip microcontrollers designed for automotive body applications.The embedded flash memory will range from 256 KB to 2 MB and packages will be covered from small package 48 pin to 176 pin.
